OL,6,FBut bigger news for him was
OL,7,Fdiscovering yesterday that his name
OL,8,Fwould finally be cleared, as it
OL,10,F"I had this news and quite frankly,
OL,11,Fthis overtook it," he told ITV Tyne
OL,12,FTees, adding: "It's not just
OL,13,Fme....There are hundreds, if not
OL,14,Fthousands out there. Sadly, some
OL,15,Faren't here to take it on."
OL,17,FNearly 1,000 sub-postmasters were
OL,18,Fprosecuted by the Post Office during
OL,19,Fthe Horizon scandal.
