OL,6,FReflecting on his own experience, Mr
OL,7,FBell said his conviction had cast a
OL,8,Fshadow over his life.
OL,10,F"I was given 200 hours of community
OL,11,Fservice and the conviction, obviously
OL,12,Fthe conviction, totally changes your
OL,13,Flife because you're limited in what
OL,14,Fsort of applications you can put in
OL,15,Ffor jobs and things you can do," he
OL,16,Fexplained.
