OL,6,F"I decided to become a driving
OL,7,Finstructor, so I took my
OL,8,Fqualifications, then the DVLA decided
OL,9,Fbecause I had a conviction, they
OL,10,Fremoved my licence - so I'm back to
OL,11,Fsquare one again.
OL,13,F"And I was thinking about my son going
OL,14,Fto university. I was thinking of trust
OL,15,Ffunds or whatever. I'm not going to be
OL,16,Fable to do any of that. I went past
OL,17,Fangry, I went past angry."
