OL,6,FThe plight of sub-postmasters and the
OL,7,FHorizon IT scandal rose to the top of
OL,8,Fthe political agenda in January
OL,9,Ffollowing the airing of the ITV drama
OL,10,FMr Bates vs. The Post Office.
OL,12,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,13,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,14,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,15,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,17,FMr Bell believes it is thanks to the
OL,18,Fseries, which prompted a national
OL,19,Foutcry, that action has been taken now.
