OL,6,F"We wouldn't be sitting here today,"
OL,7,Fhe added. "Thank goodness for Alan
OL,8,FBates."
OL,10,FWrongly convicted sub-postmasters will
OL,11,Falso receive #600,000 compensation as
OL,12,Fwell as having their convictions
OL,13,Foverturned.
OL,15,FThose who were not convicted, but who
OL,16,Fhad to make up false losses with their
OL,17,Fown money are entitled to #75,000.
