OL,6,FBut Mr Bell said no amount can truly
OL,7,Fright the wrongs.JHe continued: "The
OL,8,Fpost office has had a fantastic
OL,9,Freputation - had - but that reputation
OL,10,Fwas because of postmasters and postmen
OL,11,Fand not the people in the hierarchy
OL,12,Fthat will be making these local
OL,13,Fdecisions."
