OL,6,FThere were 983 convictions around the
OL,7,FUK linked to the faulty Horizon system
OL,8,F- and only around 100 have been
OL,9,Foverturned so far.JMinisters have said
OL,10,Fthat is not quick enough - so they
OL,11,Fwill exonerate everyone together.JThey
OL,12,Fannounced this approach in January but
OL,13,Fthen had to draw up the precise
OL,14,Flegislation, before formally
OL,15,Fintroducing it in Parliament today.
