OL,6,FSpeaking at Prime Minster's Questions
OL,7,Ftoday, Rishi Sunak said: "I want to
OL,8,Fpay tribute to all postmasters who
OL,9,Fhave campaigned tirelessly for
OL,10,Fjustice, including those who
OL,11,Ftragically won't see the justice that
OL,12,Fthey deserve.
OL,14,F"Today's legislation marks an
OL,15,Fimportant step in finally clearing
OL,16,Ftheir names and across this house, we
OL,17,Fowe it to them to progress this
OL,18,Flegislation as soon as possible before
OL,19,Fsummer recess."
OL,21,FIt is expected to become law in July.
